data.name: labelWelcome.Text
data.value:
Welcome to the Keynesian Macroeconomic Simulator of Fiscal Policy!
In this educational game, you will play the role of Bulgaria's newly appointed Minister of Finance, with a mandate of four years.
Your goal is to maintain positive Gross Domestic Product (GDP) growth, while also trying to avoid large budget deficits.
Your tools are the Effective Tax Rate and Government Spending (see below), which you are able to adjust every three months.
When you are ready to start, click the OK button to begin the simulation.
